{"title":"山野的路（外一首）","authors":["钮宇大"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":9,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山野的路（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山西黎城县 钮宇大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静静地躺在大地的怀抱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整天亲吻着车轮和脚步；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从不炫耀金子般的色彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远保持着黄土的朴素；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与榛莽为敌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同流沙搏斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用智慧与信念铺筑加固；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把苦难和不幸甩在后面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩着痛苦，寻找幸福……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果深山里没有豺狼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猎枪只同拨火棍一样；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果大海里没有风浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海燕决不会美名远扬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果夜晚同白天一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万物都不会感念太阳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果人们尝不到蜜糖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁还肯去把蜜蜂歌唱？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}